cLink":"./Mathlib/Data/Num/Bitwise.html#SNum.pred","kind":"def","line":390,"name":"SNum.pred","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover-community/mathlib4/blob/087469e24922b85cb737497c74556c7dacc01f22/Mathlib/Data/Num/Bitwise.lean#L390-L392"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Mathlib/Data/Num/Bitwise.html#SNum.succ\"><span class=\"name\">SNum</span>.<span class=\"name\">succ</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Mathlib/Data/Num/Bitwise.html#SNum\">SNum</a> → <a href=\"./Mathlib/Data/Num/Bitwise.html#SNum\">SNum</a></span></div></div>","info":{"doc":"The successor of a `SNum` (i.e. the operation adding one). ","docLink":"./Mathlib/Data/Num/Bitwise.html#SNum.succ","kind":"def","line":386,"name":"SNum.succ","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover-community/mathlib4/blob/087469e24922b85cb737497c74556c7dacc01f22/Mathlib/Data/Num/Bitwise.lean#L386-L388"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Mathlib/Data/Num/Bitwise.html#SNum.testBit\"><span class=\"name\">SNum</span>.<span class=\"name\">testBit</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Nat\">ℕ</a> → <span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Mathlib/Data/Num/Bitwise.html#SNum\">SNum</a> → <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Bool\">Bool</a></span></span></div></div>","info":{"doc":"`SNum.testBit n a` is `true` iff the `n`-th bit (starting from the LSB) of `a` is active.\nIf the size of `a` is less than `n`, this evaluates to `false`. ","docLink":"./Mathlib/Data/Num/Bitwise.html#SNum.testBit","kind":"def","line":380,"name":"SNum.testBit","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover-community/mathlib4/blob/087469e24922b85cb737497c74556c7dacc01f22/Mathlib/Data/Num/Bitwise.lean#L380-L3